00:42:41,144 --> 00:42:43,627
He looks down, he's covered in his own blood, right?

742
00:42:43,967 --> 00:42:46,229
That's my blood, that's a lot of my blood.

743
00:42:46,970 --> 00:42:47,530
What does this do?

744
00:42:47,811 --> 00:42:49,032
Well, it makes him an underdog.

745
00:42:50,033 --> 00:42:51,014
And the thing about underdogs

746
00:42:51,594 --> 00:42:54,857
is that everybody loves an underdog, right?

747
00:42:54,998 --> 00:42:55,658
So what does this do?

748
00:42:56,239 --> 00:42:57,220
It's a trick to make him likable.

749
00:42:58,518 --> 00:43:04,141
