769
00:44:00,510 --> 00:44:01,470
He laughs and he says,

770
00:44:01,650 --> 00:44:02,671
Ha ha, crap.

771
00:44:04,612 --> 00:44:04,853
Right?

772
00:44:06,153 --> 00:44:07,374
And this is all of the above.

773
00:44:07,855 --> 00:44:09,696
First of all, it's likability, because he's funny.

774
00:44:10,797 --> 00:44:13,158
And second off, it's a shared joke.

775
00:44:13,899 --> 00:44:15,900
Because he's thinking, I can't believe this,

776
00:44:16,020 --> 00:44:18,322
