787
00:44:47,922 --> 00:44:51,264
Plus as a bonus, the more basic, the more elemental the want,

788
00:44:51,304 --> 00:44:53,226
the less time you have to spend establishing it.

789
00:44:53,673 --> 00:44:55,374
Unless you run into exposition overload.

790
00:44:56,295 --> 00:45:00,238
Survive. Avenge. Escape. Avoid. Acquire.

791
00:45:01,439 --> 00:45:03,140
These are all very elemental wants.

792
00:45:03,981 --> 00:45:05,422
Very easy for people to get.

793
00:45:09,725 --> 00:45:12,227
So that's unity of purpose. Establish what they want.

794
00:45:12,808 --> 00:45:13,908
Establish why we care.

795
00:45:15,089 --> 00:45:17,131
By and large, you've built unity of purpose.

